title: Launch Roundup: SpaceX to reach its 40th Falcon 9 flight of 2024
summary: With seven Falcon 9 launches flown this month already, SpaceX’s rapid pace continues with another three flights planned for this coming week. There are two planned launches on Wednesday, April 17, from both the east and west coasts, and another on Thursday, April 18. Additionally, a Chinese Chang Zheng 2D launched on Monday.

title: Maxar eyes spring launch of long-delayed WorldView Legion satellites
summary: Maxar announced that the first two WorldView Legion satellites have arrived at Vandenberg Space Force Base in California

title: Maxar eyes summer launch of WorldView Legion imaging satellites
summary: After years of delays, Maxar Technologies is preparing for the first launch this summer of its next-generation imaging satellites WorldView Legion.
